			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "1) Go to Act 3 -> UnderCity -> Bhaal Temple Bridge\r\n2a) Use oe BTGiveBhaalAmulet to give players Bhaal Amulet.\r\nor\r\n2b) Use oe BTSetKilledGortash to set players have killed Gortash so players are invited.\r\n2c) Players start as Dark Urge origins, and therefore their Butler will be at the door letting them in.\r\n3) Go to approach and 'speak' to the door."
				},
