					"value": "The Bhaal Temple is closed off by a massive door. They are 3 ways to open the door.\r\n1) with an Bhaal Amulet, given in the Serial Killer situation\r\n2) with invitation from Orin - which is given when players killed Gortash, after she has given the players the ultimatum\r\n3) if players are the Dark Urge, their butler will freely open the doors for the players."
				}
			}
		}
	}
}